      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DAYS OF WONDER (1) took a tumble when crowded up close to the inside last time over 520m at this track. Can find winning form this time. PAX BOSTONIA (4) is an accomplished stayer with a great record at the longer races. Was too tough when scoring last time over 630m at this track in a NG (36.06). Form here at the trip excellent including four wins. Recorded the quickest time on the card last start. One of main contenders. ZIPPING EVANIA (2) filled a minor placing last start at Richmond behind Big Town Tilly (29.92) in a Grade 5. Turned chasing the leaders but kept coming. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Expected to be in the finish again. ZIPPING CRUELLA (8) has strong claims after a top-three finish last time out.",
